Version 2.11.1                                                      2012-12-02
==============================================================================

1.    NEW FEATURES

      CR20020217
      openmdx-client.jar

      The Java archive openmdx-client.jar combines the client relevant 
      content of
      * openmdx-system.jar
      * openmdx-base.jar
      * openmdx-security.jar
      
2.    CHANGES  
     
2.0.  CHANGED FEATURES
      none
             
2.1.  FIXED BUGS
      
      CR10010472
      validate() fails for Password creation. Set model properties for Credential::id
      as follows: isReadOnly=true, isDerived=false, multiplicity=0..1.  
      

2.2.  DEPRECATED FEATURES
      none
            
2.3   REMOVED FEATURES
      none


