Version 2.7.0                                                       2010-08-27
==============================================================================

1.    NEW FEATURES

      CR20019273
      Key Store Resource Adapter
      
      Setting the ManagedConnectionFactory's 'ConnectionType' property to 
      'VALIDATOR_CONNECTION' has the following effect:
      * The 'UserName' attribute is not treated as key store entry alias but 
        as certificate path validation algorithm (usually "PKIX").
      * The connections are instances of ValidatorConnection and implement
        CertificateValidator

2.    CHANGES  
     
2.0.  CHANGED FEATURES      

      CR20019273
      Key Store Resource Adapter
      
      Setting the ManagedConnectionFactory's 'ConnectionType' property to 
      'KEY_CONNECTION' is now mandatory in order to retrieve instances of
      KeyConnection.
             
2.1.  FIXED BUGS
      none

2.2.  DEPRECATED FEATURES
      none
            
2.3   REMOVED FEATURES
      none


==============================================================================
Version 2.6.4                                                       2010-08-10
==============================================================================

1.    NEW FEATURES

      CR20019276
      Connection Factory Unification
      
      org.openmdx.resource.cci.ConnectionFactory is unified the generic version
      of the former connection type specific factory interfaces.

      CR20019295
      openmdx-resource.jar
      
      The Java archive openmdx-resource.jar contains classes required by 
      different resource adapters. 

2.    CHANGES  
     
2.0.  CHANGED FEATURES      
             
      CR20019276
      JCA Naming Normalization
      
      The following classes have been renamed:
      * org.openmdx.resource.pki.keystore.ManagedKeyStoreConnectionFactory to
        org.openmdx.resource.pki.keystore.ManagedConnectionFactory
      * org.openmdx.resource.pki.keystore.KeyStoreConnectionFactory to
        org.openmdx.resource.pki.keystore.ConnectionFactory
      * org.openmdx.resource.ldap.v3.LDAPConnectionFactory to
        org.openmdx.resource.ldap.v3.ManagedConnectionFactory
      * org.openmdx.resource.ldap.v3.URLConnectionFactory to
        org.openmdx.resource.ldap.ldif.ManagedConnectionFactory
             
      CR20019195
      JCA Authentication 
      
      PasswordCredential instance is accepted only by its assigned
      persistence manager factory.  
      
2.1.  FIXED BUGS
      none

2.2.  DEPRECATED FEATURES
      none
            
2.3   REMOVED FEATURES
      
      CR20019276
      Connection Factory Unification
      
      The following interfaces have been removed in favour of
      org.openmdx.resource.cci.ConnectionFactory:
      * org.openmdx.resource.ldap.cci.ConnectionFactory
      * org.openmdx.resource.pki.cci.ConnectionFactory
      
      The following interfaces has been removed in favour of its native API:
      * org.openmdx.resource.ldap.cci.Connection


